Poynt,is,a,payment,terminal,that,connects,businesses,with,their,customers,interacting,through,a,counter,top,device,It,can,be,used,to,process,several,different,forms,of,payment,electronically,The,Poynt,API,lets,developers,integrate,their,applications,with,its,services,enabling,customers,to,make,payment,as,well,as,for,businesses,to,keep,track,of,their,productivity